reviews.review_text: Exceptional Matrix This Matrix is so wonderfully balanced between audience and soundboard. The song selection is exceptionally. The energy is on. The transition into and out of Built to Last are rather clunky, but still bold and worthy. So many classics (Althea, Bird Song, Scarlet, Fire an d Playin) played here with enthusiasm and presence. This show, as presented here, should be considered within a top 50 to top 100 all time GD show; that is if you like variations of greatness not repetition of greatness like going back to every show in 72 or 77 or 89 and 90. With that, this 89 Spring tour also is outstanding. And so on.
